{"tid":1789990,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[隨筆新詩]黎明前 光復後","createTime":"2019-12-19T16:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T21:19:47.000Z","uid":262389,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb56c672786b1ed3da5c870c71da942e18fb4bd2","tid":1789990,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"黎明前 光復後<br />\n<br />\n黎明前！<br />\n極暗，是鐵幕，遮天蔽月<br />\n極怕，是暗影，無處不在<br />\n極痛，是血淚，刻骨銘心<br />\n極累，是彼岸，望之不及<br />\n<br />\n抬頭看<br />\n天無月，尚有星，若無星，尚有我<br />\n我願化光，信念為引，血汗為薪<br />\n以火光，照前路，以餘熱，聚人心<br />\n<br />\n舉步走<br />\n血在流，未忘仇，淚在飄，未忘憂<br />\n我願化劍，正義為刃，勇氣為柄<br />\n以劍刃，開太平，以雙手，定乾坤<br />\n<br />\n光復後？<br />\n未到，用堅持，奮戰到底<br />\n未夠，用團結，凝聚力量<br />\n未知，用智慧，集思廣益<br />\n未來，用希望，共創榮光"},{"pid":"5eff87a19422ed2c53709f9c5f60e3ad952b41e9","tid":1789990,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"打咗個冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec58ec08a01aab5d120e70daf461734ecb82f84f","tid":1789990,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"oh my god"},{"pid":"71c3638405721ba19da003a989880c7b33c807a0","tid":1789990,"uid":141999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:58:45.000Z","msg":"幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd19ad2ab53ab42794ebaa160fd6b6a081dd9f00","tid":1789990,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eff87a19422ed2c53709f9c5f60e3ad952b41e9","tid":1789990,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"打咗個冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"有冇咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d090ef90a80eaea68e6560193d5466288ab16","tid":1789990,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl